headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Ocelot Penetrator
content:
Stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort, hover by the bar for a while, and then make a move on the Lucky Wheel: give it a spin to win GTA$, RP, clothes and accessories, snacks, and mystery prizes of all shapes and sizes.

This week's top prize slowly twirling on the podium adjacent is the Ocelot Penetrator, a British-made sportscar built without an ounce of subtlety anywhere in its DNA.
